data.description: Gorgeous home in Hidden Lakes community has been updated including new LVP flooring downstairs and new carpet upstairs. Kitchen has new quartz countertops (including island), sink and backsplash. There’s nothing for you to do except move-in!  Includes a formal living room, formal dining room and an office/den. The heart of this home is an expansive kitchen that includes a butler’s pantry, eating bar and informal dining area open to a cozy family room with a gas fireplace. Upstairs you’ll find four bedrooms, including the primary suite with WIC and luxury 5 pc bath. There’s another full bath and laundry room upstairs. Alley access to the 2 car garage.  Low maintenance yard. Parks and trails nearby.
